# Ignea Labs — AI Consulting Site (Puerto Rico)

## Architecture
- **Framework:** Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS (static site, no framework — keep lightweight for spotty connections in Puerto Rico)
- **Database:** None for MVP. Diagnostic answers in localStorage/sessionStorage. Future: Supabase.
- **APIs:** Google Fonts CDN (Plus Jakarta Sans + JetBrains Mono), Formspree (contact form), jsPDF (PDF report generation)
- **Styling:** Vanilla CSS with CSS custom properties. No Tailwind, no preprocessors.
- **i18n:** Custom JS i18n system using data-i18n attributes. Spanish is PRIMARY. English is secondary. Default: ES.
- **Deployment:** Vercel (static site)
- **Repo:** github.com/fede09balto-gif/onda-ai

## Design System
### Colors
- Background: `#0A0A0F` / Surface 1: `#141419` / Surface 2: `#1C1C24`
- Accent: `#E5531A` (fiery orange-red)
- Text primary: `rgba(255,255,255,0.9)` / Secondary: `rgba(255,255,255,0.65)` / Dim: `rgba(255,255,255,0.4)`
- Coral: `#E5634B` / Code purple: `#AFA9EC`

### Typography
- Display: `'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif` (400-700)
- Mono: `'JetBrains Mono', monospace` (300-700)
- H1: clamp(36px, 4.5vw, 56px). H2: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 40px). H3: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 26px).

### Visual Rules
- Border radius: 0px everywhere. Sharp corners. Engineering aesthetic.
- Buttons: min-height 48px. All tap targets: minimum 48px on mobile.
- Logo: "IGNEA" white + ".LABS" accent. Text-only, letter-spacing 3px, weight 800.

## i18n System
- All translations in `js/i18n.js`: `{ es: { "key": "value" }, en: { "key": "value" } }`
- Text elements: `<span data-i18n="key">Default Spanish text</span>`
- HTML elements: `<h1 data-i18n-html="key">Default <em>Spanish</em> text</h1>`
- Spanish ALWAYS written FIRST, English second. Default language is ES.
- localStorage keys prefixed with "ignea_"

## Pre-edit Checklist
1. Read BUILD_SPEC.md for full page specs before building any new page
2. Every new string → add to BOTH es and en in js/i18n.js. Never hardcode text.
3. Every page: shared nav, shared footer, gradient dots bg, language toggle, responsive mobile
4. Every input: dark surface bg (#141419), 1px border, accent on focus, 48px min tap target
5. Every multiple-choice option: styled as card (dark surface, border, accent on selection). No native radio/checkbox.
6. No external JS frameworks. Vanilla JS only.
7. No images for MVP — all visuals are CSS/Canvas/SVG.
8. Mobile responsive: test at 375px, 768px, 1440px.
9. Forms submit to Formspree. Show success state after submission.
10. All console.log removed before committing.

## Known Bugs
- Language toggle must restart terminal animation in correct language
- Hero CTA buttons with HTML entities (→) must use innerHTML, not textContent
- Range slider: use 'input' event, not 'change' event
- Diagnostic info collection is BEFORE questions (screen 1), not after

