## Business Context
- Puerto Rico targeting local SMBs (restaurants, clinics, hotels, law firms)
- Partner: Gatun Labs (Panama, $15-30K projects)
- Prices: $5,000-25,000 per project
- Diagnostic survey is the lead magnet and sales tool — must feel premium
- Low scores = HIGH opportunity (frame positively, never judgmentally)
- Target audience is NOT technical. Impressive but not intimidating.
- Most clients view on mobile, many on slower connections.
